
'''''Nairobi Half Life''''' ni film y'ikinamico yo muri Kenya yasohotse 2012 iyobowe na David "Tosh" Gitonga<ref>Nairobi Half Life: AFI Fest Review - The Hollywood Reporter <nowiki>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com</nowiki> › news › general-news</ref>. Iyi filime yatoranijwe nka filime yo muri kenya yinjiye neza mu rurimi rw'amahanga muri Oscar  mu bihembo bya 85 bya Osama<ref>Nairobi Half Life | IFFR <nowiki>https://iffr.com</nowiki> › iffr › films › nairobi-half-life</ref>, ariko ntiyaboneka  k'urutonde rwa nyuma, kandi ni ubwa mbere Kenya itanga filime muri iki cyiciro<ref>Awards - Nairobi Half Life (2012) - IMDb <nowiki>https://www.imdb.com</nowiki> › title › awards</ref>. Mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya 33 rya Durban, Joseph Wairimu yatsindiye igihembo cy'umukinnyi mwiza<ref>Nairobi Half Life wins 5 Awards at the Kalasha Film ... <nowiki>https://www.kenyanvibe.com</nowiki> › nairobi-half-life-wins-5-...</ref>.  Yatsindiye kandi igihembo cya Afurika Movie Academy igihembo cy'umukinnyi wizewe cyane kuva mu birori bya 9<ref>Nairobi Half Life Wins Big at The Africa Magic Viewers Choice ... <nowiki>https://nairobiwire.com</nowiki> › 2014/03 › nairobi-half-life-wi...</ref> . Yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi muri Afrika Magic Viewers Choice Awards 2014 <ref>Nairobi Half Life Bags Award in Africa Movies - allAfrica.com <nowiki>https://allafrica.com</nowiki> › stories</ref>. 

